main_body:
Each import licence application submitted in the period 1 January to 30 April 2004 in connection with the quotas referred to in Regulation (EC) No 1279/98 shall be granted for up to the following quantities:
(a) 100 % of the quantities requested of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Slovakia, the Czech Republic, Romania, Bulgaria or Hungary;
(b) 100 % of the quantities requested of products falling within CN code 1602 50 originating in Romania;
(c) 0,45080 % of the quantities requested of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Poland.
